10#include <stdio.h>
11#include "internal/cryptlib.h"
12#include <openssl/pkcs12.h>
13
14PKCS8_PRIV_KEY_INFO *PKCS8_decrypt(const X509_SIG *p8, const char *pass,
15 int passlen)
16{
17 const X509_ALGOR *dalg;
18 const ASN1_OCTET_STRING *doct;
19 X509_SIG_get0(p8, &dalg, &doct);
20 return PKCS12_item_decrypt_d2i(dalg,
21 ASN1_ITEM_rptr(PKCS8_PRIV_KEY_INFO), pass,
22 passlen, doct, 1);
23}
